summary: The candidate has strong Java and JavaScript foundations with React and Next.js experience, but lacks specific backend frameworks (Spring Boot, Hibernate), API technologies (REST, gRPC, GraphQL), several required databases, and DevOps tools mentioned in the job description.

The candidate has experience with Java, JavaScript, React, Vue, PostgreSQL, and Agile/Scrum methodologies, but lacks many required backend frameworks, database systems, DevOps tools, and specialized technologies like IBM ODM.
